import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-leave',
  templateUrl: './leave.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['./leave.page.scss'],
  standalone:false
})
export class LeavePage implements OnInit {

  constructor() { }

  ngOnInit() {
  }
 formData = {
    name: '',
    nameSecond: '',
    fromDate: '',
    toDate: '',
    totalDays: '',
    reason: '',
    approverName: 'CHETTIAPPAN .V',
  };


}
<ion-header [translucent]="true">
  <ion-toolbar >
<ion-buttons slot="start">
  <ion-back-button defaultHref="/home"></ion-back-button>
</ion-buttons>

    <ion-title>Leave</ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content [fullscreen]="true" class="ion-padding leave-application-content">
  <ion-header collapse="condense">
    <ion-toolbar>
      <ion-title size="large">Leave Application</ion-title>
    </ion-toolbar>
  </ion-header>

  <form #ondutyForm="ngForm">
    <!-- Employee Code -->
    <ion-item>
      <ion-label position="stacked">Employee Code</ion-label>
      <ion-input
        [(ngModel)]="formData.name"
        name="name"
        placeholder="EGR998"
        required>
      </ion-input>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- Employee Name -->
    <ion-item>
      <ion-label position="stacked">Employee Name</ion-label>
      <ion-input
        [(ngModel)]="formData.nameSecond"
        name="nameSecond"
        placeholder="ARAVIND G"
        required>
      </ion-input>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- From Date -->
    <ion-item lines="none">
      <ion-label position="stacked">From Date</ion-label>
      <ion-datetime-button datetime="fromDate"></ion-datetime-button>
      <ion-modal keepContentsMounted="true">
        <ng-template>
          <ion-datetime
            id="fromDate"
            presentation="date"
            [(ngModel)]="formData.fromDate"
            name="fromDate">
          </ion-datetime>
        </ng-template>
      </ion-modal>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- To Date -->
    <ion-item lines="none">
      <ion-label position="stacked">To Date</ion-label>
      <ion-datetime-button datetime="toDate"></ion-datetime-button>
      <ion-modal keepContentsMounted="true">
        <ng-template>
          <ion-datetime
            id="toDate"
            presentation="date"
            [(ngModel)]="formData.toDate"
            name="toDate">
          </ion-datetime>
        </ng-template>
      </ion-modal>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- Total Days -->
    <ion-item>
      <ion-label position="stacked">Total Days</ion-label>
      <ion-input
        [(ngModel)]="formData.totalDays"
        name="totalDays"
        type="number"
        placeholder="e.g. 2"
        required>
      </ion-input>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- Reason -->
    <ion-item>
      <ion-label position="stacked">Reason</ion-label>
      <ion-select
        [(ngModel)]="formData.reason"
        name="reason"
        placeholder="Select Reason"
        required>
        <ion-select-option value="Exam">Exam</ion-select-option>
        <ion-select-option value="Personal">Personal</ion-select-option>
      </ion-select>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- Approver Name -->
    <ion-item>
      <ion-label position="stacked">Approver Name</ion-label>
      <ion-input
        [(ngModel)]="formData.approverName"
        name="approverName"
        value="CHETTIAPPAN .V"
        required>
      </ion-input>
    </ion-item>

    <!-- Submit -->
    <ion-button expand="block" class="submit-button">
      Submit
    </ion-button>
  </form>
</ion-content>
